data.description: Nestled in a sought-after community in Gray's Creek this home features 4 bedrooms & 2.5 baths, curb appeal, covered front porch, custom exterior design & a community pool!! Enter into the two-story foyer w/ adjacent formal dining, open concept living & eat in kitchen with luxury vinyl flooring, granite countertops, expansive kitchen island & cozy fireplace! The primary bedroom is on the first floor for convenience & boasts an additional sitting area, beautiful ensuite w/ dual vanities, soaking tub, separate tiled shower & large walk-in closet. The second story features a large loft perfect for toys, movies, gaming space & more! A second full bath with dual vanities and three additional bedrooms are also located on the second floor. Out back provides the privacy of a large, fenced yard, covered patio, a fire pit for your enjoyment, a wooded lot behind & additional storage. Conveniently located to schools, dining, shopping, entertainment, healthcare facilities & Fort Liberty.
